data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. This beautiful 4 Bedroom 2 Bath home is located in the desirable subdivision Indian Trails and is ready to be moved into! This home boasts an amazing open floor plan, A spacious laundry room, and a walk-in closet.  New Roof 2022, AC 2019, Water heater 2019, All appliances 2023, and gorgeous Granite. Stunning light laminate flooring in all main living areas and carpet in bedrooms. Don’t miss out on this opportunity and make this lovely home yours. Make sure to watch the virtual tour for the perfect walkthrough of your future home!!
